On Wed, 19 Jul 2000 11:47:42 -0700 you sent this message:
>I want to implement something of a traffic smoother that instead of 
>sending packets in a burst would send them at some particular rate 
>and hence smooth it out.
Sounds like traffic shaping. I recommend looking up info on Class Based
Queuing (CBQ) and bandwidth shaping... also try Quality of Service (QoS).
This may meet your needs.
Myrddin
